'''''Codec''''' was a group of [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Class-L cargo container]]s that carried communications gear.

They were docked near [[Bretie Facility]] along with [[pressure tank]]s ''[[Nuro]]'' when the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] assaulted the facility. The Rebel forces destroyed everything in the vicinity.

